utterances.speaker: A
utterances.text: Hey there! I'm Michael Thompson, but everyone calls me Mike.

utterances.speaker: B
utterances.text: Nice to meet you, Mike! I'm Elizabeth Wilson. Most people call me Beth.

utterances.speaker: A
utterances.text: Great to meet you too, Beth. So what brings you here today?

utterances.speaker: B
utterances.text: Well, Mike, I wanted to discuss the new project we're starting.

utterances.speaker: A
utterances.text: Beth, that sounds interesting. Mike here is always excited about new projects!

utterances.speaker: B
utterances.text: I can see that, Mike! Elizabeth is pretty excited about it too.

utterances.speaker: A
utterances.text: Michael thinks this could be a game-changer, Beth.

utterances.speaker: B
utterances.text: I agree, Mike. Let's make it happen!
